Steps to integrate email with react js

1)go to the emailjs third party website and create an account from which the email will be sent
https://dashboard.emailjs.com/sign-up

2)Set up the account by logging in from your google account and design the email template

3) install emailjs package in your react app
npm i emailjs-com

4)Insert the following code in your App.js and App.css respectively
		->In App.js replace the service id,tempelate id and user id with your ids respectively
		->find your user id at -https://dashboard.emailjs.com/admin/integration
		->find your service id at -https://dashboard.emailjs.com/admin
		->find your template id at-https://dashboard.emailjs.com/admin/templates

You Are Good To Go !!  HAPPY CODING :)
